{"tid":1221652,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"被狗查的應對方法","createTime":"2019-06-14T09:08:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-02T14:44:22.000Z","uid":193565,"like":21,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"e8823fab060f2a84207c68820775d53e42553437","tid":1221652,"uid":193565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T09:08:38.000Z","msg":"今日好多狗周圍查人，屌你老母，小弟提供以下應對方法，大家集C廣益。<br />\n因應特區政府指<span style=\"color: blue;\">廣東話並非香港官方語言</span>，而香港人（包括警犬）的普通話水平參差，<span style=\"color: red;\">被查問時應使用英語對答，並說明自己不懂中文。</span><br />\n例子：<br />\n犬：喂身份證<br />\n你：Sorry sir! I don't know Chinese.<br />\n<br />\n由於大部份警犬英文水平並非human-understandable，可能需要翻譯協助，此時請勿接受路人之翻譯協助，因為<span style=\"color: red;\">未必能正確表達警犬意思</span>。為保安全，應等候警犬之同儕到來進行翻譯，過程中保持緘默，並重申：Sorry, I don't know Chinese，其後只要能夠明白其英文（例：ID card please），即可與警犬合作交出身份證。<br />\n<br />\n被搜查/查身時：<br />\n先注意：<br />\n警務人員在以下情況須出示警察委任證：<br />\n便衣警務人員：在行使警察權力時，必須表明身分及出示委任證。<br />\n軍裝警務人員：一般無須主動出示警察委任證，但如市民提出要求，他們亦須出示委任證，除非情況不容許，或要求不合理。<br />\n<br />\n對方提出要求時<span style=\"color: red;\">仍應用英文作唯一溝通語言</span>，要求其提供委任證或合理原因，例：<br />\n犬：而家要搜你身<br />\n你：Please provide a valid reason or present your warrant card.<br />\n如警犬出示委任證，注意不可觸碰，只能眼看，警犬委任證特徵如下：<br />\n正面印有(包括中英文) ： <br />\n香港警察、  <br />\n彩色警徽、  <br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">警務人員姓名、職級、僱員號碼</span>、 <br />\n相片，另有香港警察及HONG KONG POLICE 字眼的鐳射標記。 <br />\n背面印有以下聲明：「本證持有人是經正式委任的香港警察，其相片及資料載於背面。」<br />\n<br />\n[使用錄影功能保障自己]<br />\n對方提供其一後開啟你手機的錄影功能，於開始時提及其編號及姓名，說明對方即將搜查，並確保（用眼和鏡頭）對方雙手沒有任何其他物品，於搜查時確保雙眼和鏡頭全程監察，盡量不要讓其同儕碰到任何你/你的物品或要求其於1-2米外觀看，必要時透過對方尋求另一市民目證（你不懂中文），<span style=\"color: red;\">以防搜查其間無故出現不屬於你的物品</span>。<br />\n<br />\n請大家<span style=\"color: blue;\">善用權利</span>、配合調查，<span style=\"color: blue;\">必須奉公守法</span>，全程盡量避免碰到警犬身體任何一部份，<span style=\"color: red;\">特別是後面</span>，以免構成襲警罪行。<br />\n如有錯漏請指出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35c1566a572e4771aa03abc96081c7d76a2931a1","tid":1221652,"uid":193565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T09:22:36.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d15e27f72e1f3fecf0f77e30d7955a817c4d70c","tid":1221652,"uid":193565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T09:54:59.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"c4e05d399ba3b231533f90b4db5cc9b1bd2a8dc9","tid":1221652,"uid":193565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T09:57:22.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"6808ef6c62be4bcf5f6b4861342f2be377d60adf","tid":1221652,"uid":99243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T10:00:37.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"484f6063eab08f83a4aead3e899195c1bfef723f","tid":1221652,"uid":193565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T10:03:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"13f93ccfb337d63f2cfee9362629aa5a64d9b664","tid":1221652,"uid":193565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T10:18:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9518f7946dfff64e1953e0dc4b326e862cb11db4","tid":1221652,"uid":63626,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T10:20:43.000Z","msg":"用其他外語答佢會唔會直接sorry sorry,跟住走開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00b8cc1f8c889473b2a602d988d474629ddab2be","tid":1221652,"uid":42304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T10:21:58.000Z","msg":"俾人Check緊那個可以拍片？"},{"pid":"97e9c1dd700d4cb148b4e9badb84e51959ca68a7","tid":1221652,"uid":193565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9518f7946dfff64e1953e0dc4b326e862cb11db4","tid":1221652,"uid":63626,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T10:20:43.000Z","msg":"用其他外語答佢會唔會直接sorry sorry,跟住走開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T10:29:22.000Z","msg":"咁就成功洗走佢，唔走就可以拖住佢等佢冇得跑數。全程非常合作、合法"},{"pid":"2a44b39656ddf0bbebe4a66ffbd747252886db89","tid":1221652,"uid":193565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"00b8cc1f8c889473b2a602d988d474629ddab2be","tid":1221652,"uid":42304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T10:21:58.000Z","msg":"俾人Check緊那個可以拍片？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T10:30:57.000Z","msg":"搵其他幫手<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190611/59704601\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190611%2F59704601&d=%2Bo9ZPOFl8lx%2FL2stOySvpCcuUNiPSPuqsSoNSJcc%2FI4%3D&h=d8c32741\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190611%2F59704601&h=27ea8ba5\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190611/59704601</a>"},{"pid":"8e580304c3867a33709f06e729102756ab7225d4","tid":1221652,"uid":193565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T14:44:22.000Z","msg":"push"}]}